@@aMoonthread Clothier's Court@@N~
Bolts of dyed linen and rune-stitched cotton now frame this corner of Midgaard, where apprentice couriers stop to be measured beside veteran hedge-mages in need of fresh wardcloth. Tailor's bells and shearsong mingle with market noise, and mannequins in layered travel robes stand beneath practical @@ylanterns@@N while a cloth armorer displays ready stock for every discipline. The paving still bears old ward sigils, but this square now clearly serves as a bustling outfitter's court for soft armor and reinforced garments.~
