@@aIronweave Armourer's Arcade@@N~
Forged greaves and ringed harness now crowd this corner arcade, where mercenaries and caravan guards queue beside sparring veterans for fresh steel. The rhythmic clatter of rivets and the hiss of quenched plate roll out from open-front stalls lit by practical @@ylanterns@@N, while weapon racks and measuring frames line the walls in strict order. A mezzanine counter displays heavy melee panoplies by rank and campaign, marking this square as Midgaard's dedicated hall for close-combat armorers.~
